## 🛠 Customization Options

Easy to customize:

### Change Colors:
Edit CSS variables in the code:
```css
--primary: #FFCC00;  /* Change to your color */
--dark: #1a1a1a;     /* Background color */
```

### Add More Bundles:
Edit the bundles array in server.js:
```javascript
{ id: 7, size: '75GB', validity: '30 Days', price: 15000 }
```

### Change Prices:
Update the bundle prices anytime in the code.

### Add Features:
- SMS notifications
- Email receipts
- Loyalty points
- Referral system
- WhatsApp integration

