## ⚠️ Important Reminders

1. **Never share your .env file** - Contains sensitive keys
2. **Use test keys first** - Before going live
3. **Backup your code** - Use GitHub or similar
4. **Start with test mode** - Switch to live when ready
5. **Comply with regulations** - Check local requirements
6. **Have terms of service** - Protect yourself legally
7. **Keep records** - For tax and accounting purposes

